<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Avijit ❤️ Esha</title>

<style>
body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #ff758c, #ff7eb3);
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
}

header {
    padding: 30px;
}

h1 {
    font-size: 40px;
}

.heart {
    font-size: 50px;
    animation: beat 1s infinite;
}

@keyframes beat {
    0% {transform: scale(1);}
    50% {transform: scale(1.2);}
    100% {transform: scale(1);}
}

.card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    margin: 20px;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 15px;
}

footer {
    margin-top: 30px;
    padding: 15px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <h1>Avijit ❤️ Esha</h1>
    <div class="heart">❤️</div>
    <p>Forever Together</p>
</header>

<div class="card">
    <h2>💌 Relationship Date</h2>
    <p>November 11</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
    <h2>📖 First Meet</h2>
    <p>Our first introduction was on Facebook 💙</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
    <h2>💖 Message</h2>
    <p>Our love story is simple but beautiful.  
    We started as strangers and became everything for each other.</p>
</div>

<footer>
    <p>Made with ❤️ by Avijit</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
